"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**deBridge** — **一种跨链互操作性和流动性转移协议**，允许在各种区块链之间真正分散地传输任意数据和资产。deBridge智能合约的跨链互通由deBridge治理选择的独立预言机/验证器网络提供支持。\\n\\ndeBridge 项目在[Chainlink Global Hackathon](https://chain.link/hackathon)期间启动，该团队致力于解决区块链之间传输数据和流动性以及缺乏单一去中心化资产桥接标准的紧迫问题。该项目荣获大奖，并在全球140多个团队中获得第一名。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/POnTWR9kw-9ZszkXgdKlU.png?height=450&width=842)\\n\\n1\\\\.添加网络测试网：Arbitrium 测试网、币安智能链测试网、HECO 测试网、Polygon 测试网。使用chainlist一键添加\\n\\n[https://chainlist.org/](https://chainlist.org/)\\n\\n2\\\\.水龙头领测试币：ETH（Kovan）,BNB,HT，MATIC\\n\\n[https://testnet.binance.org/faucet-smart](https://testnet.binance.org/faucet-smart)\\n\\n[https://faucet.routerprotocol.com/](https://faucet.routerprotocol.com/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/DHIjg4K_xBEKAuXfoSFYU.png?height=394&width=1099)\\n\\n[https://scan-testnet.hecochain.com/faucet](https://scan-testnet.hecochain.com/faucet)\\n\\n3\\\\.进入测试网连接钱包\\n\\n[https://testnet.debridge.finance/](https://testnet.debridge.finance/)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/kvH2-Nu6_taqETPsM_uue.png?height=257&width=999)\\n\\n4\\\\.任意选择一个链进行跨链操作，输入数量，然后点击确认转账\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5j7P-aqPwL69mCFUc3gPP.png?height=709&width=1084)\\n\\n5\\\\.点击右下角的领取，可以看到进度\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/_0VTKWJo7RJ72O4OY-9z8.png?height=386&width=440)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/mbrZWG_POv-avOZfNLU8U.png?height=891&width=1266)\\n\\n其他网络跨链方式同上，本次教程到此结束。\\n\\n可以通过以下途径找到我们\\n\\nTwitter：<https://twitter.com/Baize_Research>\\nTelegram：<https://t.me/baizeblock>\\nDiscord：<https://discord.gg/2ABxxMbsps>\\n微博：<https://weibo.com/u/7731782351>\\n火信：<http://mrw.so/5vNjit>\\n微信公众号：白泽研究院\",\"timestamp\":1642313259,\"title\":\"deBridge测试网盲测教程\"},\"digest\":\"y5VmSiypJ3pnhIkoAlgDuhdz-UIQnp0V_cciWw5gToc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xdfb12bF05af4fFFbEC2837ED890B48084c1F1C43\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"AoyxhgjXD498urAKOBciS6UXRVR1W2353c6E8EIC0RQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rkMLSB-YGWqxNnpy_ocFw6N2V8FnyF72FLKr6iGjBIY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"NoioMetnKqeOZv13hGp5XKBHDz6HRKHTlNBX_laY-46rcnNp0QSLsBULFanJtMjGUKqRZA6MWBjVaDJT1dMAvg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x56afc4b0dfb558254e6f39e29e10469d06701143a0ad85421dfc6ac2d1a60bb3722fa579cfb87a357fe40d5909560b80db636a393e482e7763c155caa0bc79b91c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"AoyxhgjXD498urAKOBciS6UXRVR1W2353c6E8EIC0RQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"rkMLSB-YGWqxNnpy_ocFw6N2V8FnyF72FLKr6iGjBIY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"y5VmSiypJ3pnhIkoAlgDuhdz-UIQnp0V_cciWw5gToc\"}"